      • validatedPut

        boolean validatedPut(K key,
                     V value,
                     OIndexEngine.Validator<K,V> validator)
        Puts the given value under the given key into this hash table. Validates the operation using the provided validator.
        Parameters:
        key - the key to put the value under.
        value - the value to put.
        validator - the operation validator.
        Returns:
        true if the validator allowed the put, false otherwise.
        See Also:
        OIndexEngine.Validator#validate(Object, Object, Object)
